data.description:
This 3-bed, 2-bath Peoria home with NO HOA boasts a myriad of improvements. With vaulted ceilings, an open layout, formal dining, and a spacious great room featuring a fireplace, the home exudes modern charm. The master bedroom, strategically split for privacy, adds to the allure.
The master bathroom showcases resurfaced dual sinks, a high-tech shower display with a color-coded temperature readout.
